channel.description:
[center][size=36pt][b]ImmortalityX[/b][/size][/center] [center][b]Server Status: [size=14pt][ONLINE][/size] [center][size=14pt] A brand new runescape private server! This new server has so many [b]great features[/b] that would take the rest out of the day to type out so come check us out right now[u] you will not regret it![/u] [/size] [b]Webclient Link-[/b] https://www.rspscoding.org/play/?server=ImmortalityX [b]Downloadable Client Link-[/b] http://uppit.com/md6ikjdd77y2/ImmortalityX.jar [b]Forums Link-[/b] http://immortalityx.freeforums.org/index.php [b]Video Link-[/b] http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4vAW__2pPDk [size=24pt]Join Us You Will Not Regret It![/size]
[size=10pt][u]For more information about the server continue reading here. [/u] [b]Skills:[/b] Every skill is fully working in the game as well teleports to each skill. [b]Minigames:[/b] Dominion tower, Duel Arena, Fight Caves,Barrows, Fight Kiln. [b]Bosses:[/b] Bandos, Armadyl, Sarodomin, Zamorock, King Black dragon, Tormented demons, Queen black dragon, Corporal beast. [b]Pking:[/b] Almost every single weapon in the game with every special attack available, flawless switches, pvp teleports. [b]Events:[/b] Every second Friday there is the Champion of the duel arena meaning there is gear set in place with requirements&rules and may the best pker win the title! Hide&seek contests for prizes, Scheduled clan battles once a month and much more to come! [b]More:[/b] Loyalty points, Squeel of fortune, special donator city, donator gear, Full screen HD client, Fully Working map and more for you to come check out. [/size]
[/center] __________________

item.dc:creator: @Elrick Elrick
item.description:
@Elrick wrote:

This is something I can get behind, but I really hope to see your teleports eventually phased out, especially for skilling. If you just give direct access to skills then you make it too easy to make skilling even worth training unless it is the only way to obtain specific items. I can understand having a teleport that takes you to maybe the rope of God Wars, but I hope for your sake it isn’t straight into their lairs.

These are just my opinions, so either way good luck!
